Public schema tables (all have RLS enabled; current row count reported as 0):

- public.multiplayer_sessions  
  - PK: id  
  - FKs: story_version_id → public.story_versions.id; host_id → public.users.id  
  - Notable columns: status enum (pending/active/completed, default pending), settings jsonb, session_state jsonb, version int default 0, created_at/updated_at timestamptz

- public.saves  
  - PK: id  
  - FKs: story_id → public.stories.id; user_id → public.users.id  
  - Notable columns: save jsonb, mode text default 'solo' with check (solo|multiplayer), created_at/updated_at timestamptz

- public.stories  
  - PK: id  
  - FK: created_by → public.users.id  
  - Notable columns: slug text UNIQUE, title, summary nullable, created_at/updated_at timestamptz

- public.story_versions  
  - PK: id  
  - FK: story_id → public.stories.id  
  - Notable columns: status enum (draft/published, default draft), outline jsonb, published_at nullable, component_lock jsonb, engine_range text, shell jsonb default {"key":"shell.ebook"}, theme text, created_at/updated_at timestamptz

- public.users  
  - PK: id  
  - FK: id → auth.users.id  
  - Notable columns: username nullable, avatar_url nullable, created_at/updated_at timestamptz
